# Node.js
node_modules/       → ignores all Node packages
npm-debug.log       → ignores npm debug logs
.env                → ignores environment variable files (secret keys)

# Capacitor / Android / iOS
android/            → ignores the Android build folder
ios/                → ignores the iOS folder
*.iml               → ignores IDE project files
.gradle/            → ignores Gradle caches
build/              → ignores build outputs
.idea/              → ignores IntelliJ / WebStorm project files

# Optional
.DS_Store           → ignores Mac system files
